{
  "stem": "22883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my participation in that was just to be a link in a-- in a chain of trafficking arms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I had such a-- a position that I-- I had in my office where I was working at desk, very close to the entrance.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So from the street, you could just open the door, and there was my desk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So somebody was coming and leaving in the drawer of half-opened drawer in my desk, a package.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't look what it was in the package because I knew there is something, the ammunition or a revolver or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- there was the arms, the small arms smuggled to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after a few hours or-- or even sometimes the next day, there was coming the other person and was also result of asking any questions, and any talk, was grabbing this package and going away.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but I knew that this person was another link in-- in the smuggling of-- of arms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was my participation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I gave the-- the desk and the drawer and the access to it in order to transfer from one person to another person.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In a few-- in a few cases, in a few cases, I was introduced to somebody who needs-- who needed a-- a-- a document.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or you see, sometimes Jewish people, they could obtain identification document which was not completed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For example, there was no photograph there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, if there was no photograph, there was no stamp, which, you know, one part-- on one part of that stamp goes on the photograph, the other one on the document itself.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I did myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
